com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.aspera.transfer

Interface AsperaTransfer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AsperaTransaction
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AsperaTransactionImpl

    public interface AsperaTransfer
    Class which provides access to the progress & status of a transfer. This object is returned to the user when any transfer process is started.
